<plot>Local talk and variety show that ABC picked up for only one season. It was picked up again a couple of years later by DuMont. Continued locally for another 23 years. Some of the regulars also appeared on two other locally produced shows, Ruth Lyons 50-50 club and Midwestern Hayride. All produced in Cincinnati, Ohio.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581734</url></doc>
